parameters.name: BX
parameters.description:
JMXYZ X component of the magnetic-field in nT.                          
      X is in the plane containing Z and the IAU_JUPITER (S3 1997)            
      Prime Merdian.

parameters.name: BY
parameters.description:
JMXYZ Y component of the magnetic-field in nT.                          
      Y completes the right handed set (Z x X).

parameters.name: BZ
parameters.description:
JMXYZ Z component of the magnetic-field in nT.                          
      Z is the Jupiter dipole.

parameters.name: BTOTAL
parameters.description:
Average value of the full-resolution magnetic-field magnitudes          
      calculated over the averaging interval in nT. Note that this value      
      may differ slightly from the square root of the sum of the squares      
      of the averaged field components.

parameters.name: NPTS
parameters.description: Number of points in the average.
